page.title: 06FASHIONS
page.content: The fashions I like best are jeans and tops but I also wear nice clothes like quite shhort mini-skirts which are black leather and I wear a stud belt with them. And I have got a disco dress which is black with dots on and sequins around the top.And I also wear nice jogging suits and all-in-one suits,the last one I had was white with black lines on it. I wear high healed shoes and I have had a new pair which are white with plated sides.And I like low back dresses and I have got two.Ialso like flick back hair styles.My freind Rebecca also likes jeans and tops but she doesn't like low back dresses or high heals and she also doesn't like mini skirts thats the fashions I like.
